            <title>[LU-2957] Proc tnable to control RAS_INCREASE_STEP</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2957</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Recent 4M debacle highlighted the problems with RAS_INCREASE_STEP that is dependent on blkbits.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So would not it make sense to expose either that or RAS_INCREASE_STEP as a proc tunable? I definitely think different people will have different requirements in regards to that functionality and so the tunable makes total sense&lt;/p&gt;</description>
